OL,3,CMan charged in connection with church
OL,4,C'hate crime' on Good Friday
OL,6,FA man has been charged after "obscene"
OL,7,Fgraffiti was sprayed over a church and
OL,8,Fnearly 40 gravestones on Good Friday.
OL,10,FLewd images and offensive phrases were
OL,11,Fdaubed on the walls and gravestones of
OL,12,FSt James Church in Leyland, near
OL,13,FPreston, on 18 April, forcing the
OL,14,Fchurch to hide the graffiti with
OL,15,Fplants before a wedding on Saturday.
OL,17,FFollowing the incident Lancashire
OL,18,FPolice said the "disgraceful act of
OL,19,Fvandalism" was "being treated as a
OL,20,Fhate crime".
