OL,3,CMan charged in connection with church
OL,4,C'hate crime' on Good Friday
OL,6,FJoseph Williams, 30, has now been
OL,7,Fcharged with 10 criminal damage
OL,8,Foffences which include two offences of
OL,9,Freligiously aggravated criminal damage
OL,10,Fin relation to the damage to St James
OL,11,FChurch, as well as an attack on nearby
OL,12,FSt Mary's Church on 27 April.
OL,14,FThe other charges relate to seven
OL,15,Fcounts of criminal damage to motor
OL,16,Fvehicles which occurred over two
OL,17,Fnights from 18 to 20 April, and one
OL,18,Fcharge of criminal damage to property
OL,19,Fwhereby a garden gate has been spray
OL,20,Fpainted.
