OL,3,CMan charged in connection with church
OL,4,C'hate crime' on Good Friday
OL,6,FHe is due to appear at Preston
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court.
OL,9,FDespite the vandalism, St James' Vicar
OL,10,FMarc Wolverson says those in the local
OL,11,Fcommunity came together to help remove
OL,12,Fsome of the offensive messages,
OL,13,Fallowing the church to celebrate the
OL,14,FEaster weekend.
OL,16,FSpeaking at the time he said it was
OL,17,F"the worst thing I've had to deal with
OL,18,Fas a vicar".
