OL,3,CMan charged in connection with church
OL,4,C'hate crime' on Good Friday
OL,6,F"My first reaction was heartbreak at
OL,7,Fthe actions of these individuals who
OL,8,Fperpetrated this crime; I feel very
OL,9,Fsorry for them," he said.
OL,11,F"But, in the days since, the way we
OL,12,Fhave seen the people of Leyland rally
OL,13,Fround to help has been so uplifting.
OL,15,F"The wedding we had planned on
OL,16,FSaturday was able to go ahead and we
OL,17,Fhave continued with all our services
OL,18,Facross the Easter weekend... one of
OL,19,Fthe holiest periods in the Christian
OL,20,Fcalendar."
